reviews.text: Prelep muzej, svako ko dodje u Kragujevac treba da ga obidje
Sve preporuke svakom ko ima da odvoji sat vremena u Kragujevcu. Odlicna postavke, ali i sama arhitektura zdanja je ocaravajuca... Imacete osecaj kao da ste u starom Londonu.
Istorijat naj sterije vojne industrije na Balkanu,stara 160 godina.
Sve o istoriji industijalizacije grada Kragujevca. Kako su nastajala moderna oružja. Vredi pogledati.

Najstariji objekat koji reprezentuje industrijsku arhitekturu juzno od Save i Dunava iz devetnestog veka. Ambijentalno i konturno izvanredan. Neuredjen i zapusten. Povremeno ali nedovoljno u funkciji kulture
Nice gallery. Visited classical concert. Gallery looks much better inside then outside.

The coke machine is always broken, service is crapy, and the wait is not worth the food. You could go somewhere for better food and get it faster. If you are in a rush go somewhere else, this place is not worth it. To top it all off it is not kid friendly anymore. They have electronic devices that don’t even work half the time. I went once and a baby got run over by a high chair. NOT kid friendly at all.
My weakness! Always a crowd but worth the wait. This location one of the cleanest for being so busy.
Wow looks really nice, so modern, good customer service and they have some good deals.

Nasty food..filthy restaurant .. I am so fed up with the sorry excuse for customer service. I came in today and ordered chicken nuggets, no dipping sauce but 2 packs of mayo, they charged me for the mayo, then tried to give me someone elses food. after they handed my food to the car in front of me, they gave me the same food without replacing it. This place is a horrible location. I will never go back to this location. The sad thing is the owners could care less.

I would rate this place with zero stars if it was possible. We waited for the waiter for at least 30 minutes and nobody came until we alarmed the manager and then waited for another 10-15 minutes. On top of it all, when the waiter came he was rude and when we wanted to order he told  us that the coffee machine was broken and we can have only a few things from  the menu. I strongly suggest changing the whole staff asap!
The food was very good but we waited longer than acceptable for it.
